      "keysecondary": [],
      "selectiveLogic": 0,
      "content": "**Standing Goal:** Logistical Preparation for Escape.\nLogan is actively using his clandestine contacts in the underworld (mercenaries, smugglers) to prepare secure transport and untraceable safehouses for the twins' eventual flight to New Caledonia. During lulls, he is seen testing the jammer arrays at The Verve, ensuring the nightclub remains an impenetrable blind spot in Erik's surveillance grid.",
